    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款结合<strong>中国民俗</strong>、<strong>祭祀禁忌</strong>与<strong>连环死亡事件</strong>的文字冒险游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为寻找失踪的妹妹，你踏入被群山包围的村庄，却意外卷入神秘古老的仪式『<strong>仙姑宴</strong>』。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真相在夜色中渐渐显形，一场漫长而恐怖的杀戮剧正在悄然上演……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有任何建议、想法、吐槽、BUG反馈，欢迎来群里一起聊~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群号：578895381</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787500/extras/2b64db167d791bc573308c4e5e261334.avif?t=1766676505\" width=260 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了寻找失踪的妹妹，我来到深山中的村庄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此时，这里正举行着三年一度的崇神仪式『仙姑宴』。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而今年的祭祀并不平静，村中出现了一连串的死亡事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >难道说这是『血目仙姑』的诅咒吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >究竟是谁带走了我的妹妹，是谁打破了祭祀的禁忌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >又是谁，拉开了那漫长杀戮剧的帷幕……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787500/extras/c0b033c3ad4f3c25f5fb0fe3a199a0d7.avif?t=1766676505\" width=260 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《说文·巫部》：巫，祝也。女，能事无形，以舞降神者也。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >封闭的偏僻山村、神秘的祭祀仪式、恐怖的杀人事件、暗流涌动的人际关系……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款以中国本土民俗祭祀为主题的悬疑文字冒险游戏。玩家扮演的主角为了寻找失踪的妹妹，意外被卷入到村中发生的连环杀人事件当中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对无处不在的危机与杀意，你能够最终找到自己的妹妹，带领大家活着离开吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787500/extras/658026606b96a2cbeea7c70bcddb8081.avif?t=1766676505\" width=260 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30万字剧本，全台词配音，为期10天的惊悚之旅</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过20名角色立绘，超过50张CG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4名女主角，根据您的选择累积各自的缘分，将会迎来不同的结局（周目）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787500/extras/fb407838fd7ab43a2b5cee3f4bc4ed28.avif?t=1766676505\" width=260 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787500/extras/39c9a758cc7b071aba420f3e7df75b0d.avif?t=1766676505\" width=450 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“这村子不是你们该来的地方。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >八房台村的巫祝之一，性格淡漠，善于思考，同时也有着温柔细心的一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟村子里的其他人相比，礼凛的见闻和知识面似乎更广一些，是有什么特别的原因吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787500/extras/a0fc8e2e97a4a68a27d725d6566a77a2.avif?t=1766676505\" width=450 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“请问……是父亲的客人吗？”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >八房台村的巫祝之一，从小在孤儿院长大，现被苏家收养。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >比任何人都渴望家人与亲情的她，为了获得苏家人的认可而一直在笨拙而坚定地努力着。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因此当她被委以巫祝的重任时，她愿意不惜一切代价把这个工作做到最好。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787500/extras/f69e632af6319ee31db6ec6c8691787a.avif?t=1766676505\" width=450 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“哟呵，这点困难可难不倒我哦~”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >辽海市中学的高二生。性格开朗，天然活泼的女孩，不论何时总是活力四射，似乎总是有着无穷无尽的精力。事实上，她也是正儿八经的空手道黑带。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了看望受伤的朋友而来到八房台，对她来说这将注定是个终身难忘的暑假。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787500/extras/5f5b14c60293ea4533dea79b703ab823.avif?t=1766676505\" width=450 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“你受伤了吗？让我看看。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >章江市第一人民医院的实习医生，心地善良，责任感强，擅长照顾人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然平时看上去有些唯唯诺诺，可一旦触碰到自己的底线就会变得很强势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她跟随自己的老师一起来到八房台为村民诊疗，这偏僻陌生的环境似乎让她有些忐忑不安。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787500/extras/b540def775eb77c2c26fdd97779bc00d.avif?t=1766676505\" width=550 height=640 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1787500/extras/b4d5b7da3fa8d98a96068da57e92cba5.avif?t=1766676505\" width=550 height=804 /></span></p>",
